content.rendered:
Directed by J.B. Murali Krishna.

Written by Darling Swamy.

Cast Sumanth Ashwin(Ravi). Prabhakar(Seshu). Pooja Jhaveri(Kalyani) .Karuna Bhushan.Dhanraj.Pavani Gangireddy.Jeeva. Nassar((as Nasser)).Rajyalakshmi.Thagubothu Ramesh.Bharath Reddy.Shakalaka Shankar.Sudha.Meesam Suresh.Jaya Vani.Vinodh

Language Telugu.

Producers Vamsi Krishna J.

Production Sri Satya Entertainments.
